definitions.definition: A machine or device that converts other energy forms into mechanical energy, or imparts motion .
A motor car , or automobile , sometimes extended to other powered vehicles, such as goods vehicles.
examples: Motor insurance is expensive for youngsters.

definitions.definition: A source of power for something; an inspiration ; a driving force.
Any protein capable of converting chemical energy into mechanical work.
The controller or prime mover of the universe; God .
The fermenting mass of fruit that is the basis of pruno , or "prison wine".

main_definition: A machine or device that converts other energy forms into mechanical energy, or imparts motion .
secondary_definitions: ( now colloquial outside attributive use ) A motor car , or automobile , sometimes extended to other powered vehicles, such as goods vehicles.
( figuratively ) A source of power for something; an inspiration ; a driving force.
Any protein capable of converting chemical energy into mechanical work.
( Christianity , archaic , poetic ) The controller or prime mover of the universe; God .
